title: Most googled hotel-related keywords in the United Kingdom ( UK ) in January 2016
summary: The Most googled Hotel in the keywords United was Hotel Cheap_hotels , who made 3059.58 thousands .
The most googled Hotel was Last_minute_hotels , with just 40.5 thousands .

In second place was Hotel Hotels_in_London with 90.5 thousands ; third place went to Hotel Hotels with 201.0 thousands ; fourth place went to Hotel Other_related_keywords with 3059.58 thousands and fifth place went to Hotel London_hotels , who was 74.0 thousands .
gold: This statistic displays the most googled hotel-related keywords on Google UK in January 2016 . Most searched was the term `` hotels `` which was searched 201 thousand times that month . Second most popular was `` hotels in london `` .
